  "content": "# M4.5: CUDA Toggle Implementation Plan\n\n### Task 1: Add `cuda` feature gate to corvia-inference\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `crates/corvia-inference/Cargo.toml`\n\n**Step 1: Add the feature section**\n\nAdd this to the end of `crates/corvia-inference/Cargo.toml`:\n\n```toml\n[features]\ndefault = []\ncuda = [\"fastembed/cuda\"]\n```\n\n**Step 2: Verify it compiles without the feature (CPU-only, no change in behavior)**\n\nRun: `cargo check -p corvia-inference`\nExpected: success, no warnings related to features\n\n**Step 3: Commit**\n\n```bash\ngit add crates/corvia-inference/Cargo.toml\ngit commit -m \"feat(inference): add cuda cargo feature gate for GPU-accelerated ONNX inference\"\n```\n\n---\n\n\n### Task 2: Add `enable_cuda` function to corvia-workspace.sh\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `.devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh` (in corvia-workspace repo root, NOT repos/corvia)\n\nThe file is at: `/root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace/.devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh`\n\n**Step 1: Add the CUDA helper functions**\n\nInsert the following block after the `disable_surrealdb()` function (after line 137, before `# --- Status ---`):\n\n```bash",
